name: crazy monkey
description:
We take great pride in these shirts. Each one is hand-printed by us using only water-based inks. It looks better, doesn't crack and is easier on mother earth than the alternative plastisol inks. This shirt is printed on heathered American Apparel 50/50 poly cotton shirts. 

The unisex shirts are great for both men and women. The difference between the unisex shirt and the women's fit shirt is that they'll be a little longer in over all length and sleeve, a smaller crew neck, and a little looser through the mid section. So ladies, you may want to order a size smaller than you normally would if you choose to  go with a unisex option.
